  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"TABLE GAME END\"</strong> is a nostalgic adventure game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393090/extras/9f6c72fb80683f6448aad44a48683c17.avif?t=1761521296\" width=616 height=158 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After school, as always, I talk with <i>her</i> in the old school building.<br>We chat about the game she’s making, or about the things happening in the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through the window, the sunset paints the sky, and I can see someone playing in the schoolyard.<br>We just watch the scene or reminisce about old memories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quiet, peaceful days pass by, without anything particularly eventful happening.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But… <i>she</i> has already passed away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393090/extras/e19257dab3e1438177f2e8d46950a504.avif?t=1761521296\" width=616 height=158 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A walking simulator where various events unfold as you explore.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progress the story by examining objects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No quest markers or time limits, allowing for a relaxed gameplay experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>She</i> wants to spend time with you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playtime:</strong> 10–30 minutes</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Video Streaming Guidelines</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Streaming is allowed without prior permission for both individuals and organizations.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"TABLE GAME END\"</strong> is a nostalgic adventure game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393090/extras/9f6c72fb80683f6448aad44a48683c17.avif?t=1761521296\" width=616 height=158 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After school, as always, I talk with <i>her</i> in the old school building.<br>We chat about the game she’s making, or about the things happening in the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through the window, the sunset paints the sky, and I can see someone playing in the schoolyard.<br>We just watch the scene or reminisce about old memories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quiet, peaceful days pass by, without anything particularly eventful happening.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But… <i>she</i> has already passed away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393090/extras/e19257dab3e1438177f2e8d46950a504.avif?t=1761521296\" width=616 height=158 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A walking simulator where various events unfold as you explore.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progress the story by examining objects.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No quest markers or time limits, allowing for a relaxed gameplay experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>She</i> wants to spend time with you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playtime:</strong> 10–30 minutes</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ Video Streaming Guidelines</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Streaming is allowed without prior permission for both individuals and organizations.</p></li></ul>",
